'''2016年世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛'''是第17届[[世界速度滑冰锦标赛|世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛]]，于2016年2月11日至14日在俄罗斯科洛姆纳速度滑冰中心进行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://static.isu.org/media/1002/announcement-world-single-distances-ss-champs-2016-kolomna.pdf |title=ISU World Single Distances Speed Skating Championships 2016, Kolomna, Russia |publisher=[[国际滑冰联盟|International Skating Union]] |access-date=2016-02-10 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311172946/http://static.isu.org/media/1002/announcement-world-single-distances-ss-champs-2016-kolomna.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-11}}</ref>。这是俄罗斯第二次举办单程距离速度滑冰世锦赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1034477/russia-interested-in-hosting-isu-world-single-distances-speed-skating-championships-for-third-time|title=Russia interested in hosting ISU World Single Distances Speed Skating Championships for third time|work=Inside the Games|date=2016-02-17|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220134932/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1034477/russia-interested-in-hosting-isu-world-single-distances-speed-skating-championships-for-third-time|archivedate=2016-02-20}}</ref>。

